title: Momo Wholefood Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Raw, Western, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Its whole food menu is around 90% vegetarian. Makes its own raw vegan cakes and slices along with vegan muffins and cakes, cashew cheese, vegan burger, veggie bowl, daily salads and specials. Has bonsoy and organic almond milk for coffee, chai, and smoothies.
